title: Viduthalai Part 1
subTitle: A newly appointed police inspector finds himself in an ethical quandary when he is tasked with hunting down the leader of a fearsome separatist group.

title: Chingaari
subTitle: A novice postmaster in Rangpur unexpectedly becomes entangled in the complex lives of local sex workers, challenging his preconceptions.

title: Taqdeer Ka Tamasha
subTitle: An officer has a strained relationship with his brother Satya, a criminal. While attempting to gather evidence against a goon, he meets his sibling. But, they are not aware of the gangster's secrets.

title: Sikandar Sadak Ka
subTitle: When Sikander, a union worker, tries to stop his employer's misdeeds, the authorities jail him. After his release, Sikander is determined to seek revenge.

title: Jaagruti
subTitle: Sevalal, a corrupt minister, kills Vishal, an honest police officer. So Vishal's brother Jugnu vows to avenge his death.

title: Kyon Ki
subTitle: In the chaotic environment of a faraway psychiatric hospital, love blossoms between a closed-off doctor and a rebellious patient with a troubled past.

title: No Entry
subTitle: A gorgeous club dancer's ill-timed rendezvous opens up a Pandora's box of lies, absurdities and misunderstandings in the lives of three quirky couples.

title: Baaghi: A Rebel for Love
subTitle: The son of a colonel falls in love with a young woman from a brothel. However, their love soon becomes synonymous with rebellion because of social taboos.

title: Insaniyat
subTitle: Inspector Amar must unite two rival crime bosses from different religious backgrounds to fight terrorism. In the process, he discovers the personal cost of being an honest cop.

title: Insaniyat
subTitle: Inspector Amar must unite two rival crime bosses from different religious backgrounds to fight terrorism. In the process, he discovers the personal cost of being an honest cop.

title: Rajkumar
subTitle: A prince returns finally from abroad and finds an opportunity to prove himself when he discovers a dangerous plot against his family.

title: Hatya: The Murder
subTitle: Ravi's father, Ratan, gets killed when he refuses to sell his land to Murugan, a wealthy businessman. Later, Ravi sets out to avenge the death of his father.

title: Wafadaar
subTitle: Chanda's parents disapprove of her boyfriend Ranga and want her to marry Prasad. Ranga is accused of having an affair with Sita.

title: 15th August
subTitle: Nagpal kills Chaudhry and his son, Ram, a military officer. Chaudhry's second son, Vikram, vows to destroy Nagpal who is all set to become the Chief Minister on the upcoming Indian Independence Day.

title: Mela
subTitle: Best mates Kishen and Shankar decide to help village belle Roopa avenge her family's death, but their friendship is tested in the process.

title: Teri Meherbaniyan
subTitle: Ram, an honest man, falls in love with a woman named Bijli and goes on to help the people of her village. However, the region's corrupt leader, Thakur Vijay Singh, soon begins to plot against him.

title: Main Tera Dushman
subTitle: When a Forest Officer, Kishan Srivastav, hinders the criminal activities of Thakur Dayalu, he is framed for murder and sent to jail. Later, Kishan escapes prison and tries to clear his name.

title: Mr. Natwarlal
subTitle: When Natwar's elder brother is framed for bribery, he decides to avenge his brother's humiliation and thus poses as a crime lord.

title: Mr. Natwarlal
subTitle: When Natwar's elder brother is framed for bribery, he decides to avenge his brother's humiliation and thus poses as a crime lord.

title: Yes Boss
subTitle: Rahul's boss, Siddharth, is a womaniser who exploits Rahul into helping him win over Seema. However, Rahul ends up falling for Seema and is torn between his career aspirations and her.

title: Khel
subTitle: Three fraudsters trick a rich elderly woman, Sulakshana, who is desperately looking for her long-lost grandchild, in order to acquire her estate and property.

title: Mera Karam Mera Dharam
subTitle: Ajay, a businessman, provides funds to Sarjuprasad to develop his hometown. When he learns that the money has been misappropriated by Sarjuprasad, he resolves to set things right.

title: Zakhmi Aurat
subTitle: Determined to exact revenge on the goons who gangraped her, Inspector Kiran Dutt, takes matters into her own hands as the law fails to give her justice.

title: Majaal
subTitle: Vijay Kumar, an orphan, is brought up by an advocate. While he falls in love with his daughter and marries her, he struggles to cope with the humiliation he faces from her family.

title: Aao Pyaar Karen
subTitle: Just like his father before him, wealthy Raja wants to marry a poor girl but his grandmother opposes the match. The cycle of estrangement repeats itself as he chooses love over money.

title: Divya Shakti
subTitle: A young reporter, Prashant Verma, tired of injustice, bears witness to a murder case and wages war against Tau. But in the process, his life and family members get threatened.

title: Aasman Se Ooncha
subTitle: Inspector Malik transfers to Mumbai along with his family and sets out on a mission to catch King, an underworld leader. However, a shocking revelation changes the course of their lives.
